      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exceptional vehicle, a true standout that remains in showroom condition. Meticulously maintained and preserved to the highest standards, it offers a level of refinement and mechanical integrity that is increasingly rare to find. Every surface, from the flawless paintwork to the pristine interior, reflects a history of dedicated care. This is more than just a car; it is a testament to quality and a premier choice for the buyer who accepts only the best. Experience the drive of a practically new vehicle at a compelling value.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
